- ■ 30% of women among managers and professionals;
- ■ 4,300 employees contribute to innovation;
- ■ Long-term shareholders, of which 470,000 are individual shareholders;
- ■ Collaboration with tens of thousands of suppliers and more than 300 innovation partnerships with academics, industrial partners and start-ups;
