## AIR LIQUIDE BUSINESS:

## Gas, technologies and services for industry and health

The Group is a world leader in gas, technologies and services for industry and healthcare and supports the growth of nearly all economic sectors by drawing on its extensive scientific and technical expertise. Its offering includes:

- ■ The production and valorization of molecules;
- ■ The integration and marketing of proprietary technologies;
- ■ The provision of related services and digital solutions.

